author: rich
msg: Fix for http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/BEEHIVE-589 : Control fields cannot be inherited in page flows
This change causes control client initializers to be generated for any class that can *inherit* an annotated control field.  It fixes the InheritControls BVT in netui.
tests: drt in trunk, bvt in netui (WinXP)
